363
00:24:15,604 --> 00:24:20,286
at the same result in

364
00:24:20,308 --> 00:24:23,666
the end. So there is only one possible outcome of

365
00:24:23,688 --> 00:24:27,314
the collaboration. So for example, if you have a

366
00:24:27,352 --> 00:24:31,650
user that makes a change on a paragraph, and another user that deletes it,

367
00:24:31,800 --> 00:24:35,714
the cryptpad algorithm will choose a

368
00:24:35,752 --> 00:24:39,574
path that will be the same on

369
00:24:39,612 --> 00:24:42,806
all clients. And so either it will be

370
00:24:42,828 --> 00:24:46,406
considered that the change was

371
00:24:46,428 --> 00:24:49,958
done before the deletion, either it will be considered

372
00:24:49,974 --> 00:24:53,846
that deletion is done before the change, and in the end you'll

